           <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Precious Madness: Augusto Monterroso’s <em>The Rest Is Silence</em></h1>
      
          
    
          <div class="date-display-single">March 12, 2025</div>
    
          <div class="field-name-field-author field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix">
        <div class="field-label"><em>by</em>&nbsp;
